bsp;本公式假设：Bm=0.3T,&amp;nbsp; Lg/Le=0.5%=气隙长度/磁芯等效长度；&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;如果Lg/Le=气隙长度/磁芯等效长度=1%时，又如何计算呢？（请考虑）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;输出功率、磁芯截面积和开关频率决定气隙&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;，因为在反激式开关电源中气隙的体积大小决定储能的多少，频率决定能量传输的快慢；&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;如：EI25Ve=2050mm³，Ae=42平方毫米，Le=49.4mm；f=40KHz；η=0.75；&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Lg= 0.005*49.4 = 0.247mm---气隙长度&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Pin =Ve*F/5555 = 2050*40/5555 =14.76W；&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Pout =η*Pin= 0.75 * 14.76 = 11.07W;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;若：f=100KHz&amp;nbsp;则：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Pout= 11.07W *(100/40) = 27.675W;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;反激式&lt;a data-mid=&quot;1&quot; href=&quot;http://www.szsanyi.com/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration-line: none;&quot;&gt;开关电源&lt;/a&gt;设计的思考一&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;对一般变压器而言，原边绕组的电流由两部分组成，一部分是负载电流分量，它的大小与副边负载有关；当副边电流加大时，原边负载电流分量也增加，以抵消副边电流的作用。另一部分是励磁电流分量，主要产生主磁通，在空载运行和负载运行时，该励磁分量均不变化。&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;励磁电流分量就如同抽水泵中必须保持有适量的水一样，若抽水泵中无水，它就无法产生真空效应，大气压就无法将水压上来，水泵就无法正常工作；只有给水泵中加适量的水，让水泵排空，才可正常抽水。在整个抽水过程中，水泵中保持的水量又是不变的。这就是，励磁电流在变压器中必须存在，并且在整个工作过程中保持恒定。&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;正激式变压器和上述基本一样，初级绕组的电流也由励磁电流和负载电流两部分组成；在初级绕组有电流的同时，次级绕组也有电流，初级负载电流分量去平衡次级电流，激励电流分量会使磁芯沿磁滞回线移动。而初次级负载安匝数相互抵消，它们不会使磁芯沿磁滞回线来回移动，而励磁电流占初级总电流很小一部分，一般不大于总电流10％，因此不会造成磁芯饱和。&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;反激式变换器和以上所述大不相同，反激式变换器工作过程分两步：&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;第一：开关管导通，母线通过初级绕组将电能转换为磁能存储起来；&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;第二：开关管关断，存储的磁能通过次级绕组给电容充电，同时给负载供电。&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;可见，反激式变换器开关管导通时，次级绕组均没构成回路，整个变压器如同仅有一个初级绕组的带磁芯的电感器一样，此时仅有初级电流，转换器没有次级安匝数去抵消它。初级的全部电流用于磁芯沿磁滞回线移动，实现电能向磁能的转换；这种情况极易使磁芯饱和。&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;磁芯饱和时，很短的时间内极易使开关管损坏。因为当磁芯饱和时，磁感应强度基本不变，dB/dt近似为零，根据电磁感应定律，将不会产生自感电动势去抵消母线电压，初级绕组线圈的电阻很小，这样母线电压将几乎全部加在开关管上，开关管会瞬时损坏。&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;由上边分析可知，反激式开关电源的设计，在保证输出功率的前提下，首要解决的是磁芯饱和问题。&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;如何解决磁芯饱和问题？磁场能量存于何处？将在下一篇文章：反激式开关电源变压器设计的思考二中讨论。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;反激式开关电源设计的思考二---气隙的作用&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;“反激式开关电源设计的思考一”文中，分析了反激式变换器的特殊性防止磁&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;芯和的重要性，那么如何防止磁芯的饱和呢？大家知道增加气隙可在相同ΔB的&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;情况下，ΔIW的变化范围扩大许多,为什么气隙有此作用呢?&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;由全电流定律可知:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/3nJjpKuusmehmfI7EU5EDlc7Adh5lTXuAwWeicmQ7glfL9m7UzRRTVnJnzs4uYUuEYEW7hHiaCSxKMjX8U4tA20w/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; list-style: none; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; text-indent: 0em; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;由上例可知，同一个磁芯在电流不变的条件下，仅增加1mm气隙，加气隙的磁&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;感强度仅为不加气隙的磁感应强度的4.8%，看来效果相当明显。&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;加了气隙后，是否会影响输出功率呢？换句话说，加了气隙变压器还能否储&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;原来那些能量呀？看一下下面的例子就知道了：&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;在“思考一”一文中已讨论过，当开关管导通时，次级绕组均不构成&amp;nbsp;回路，此&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;时，变压器象是仅有一个初级绕组带磁芯的电感器一样，母线将次级需要的全部&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;能量都存在这个电感器里。如下图1就是一个有气隙的电感器：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.szsanyi.com/storage/521/weixin/1803/21/6d5670b79b3f85525096e4b7c7ea1c2a.png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; list-style: none; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; text-indent: 0em; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;图1表示一个磁芯长为lm，气隙长为lg，截面积为Ae的磁芯，在其上绕N匝线圈，&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;当输入电压为Ui时，输入功率为Wi：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.szsanyi.com/storage/521/weixin/1803/21/10ac06fe36e57ff99e8d9adafb2d2621.png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; list-style: none; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; text-indent: 0em; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;6式右边的积分为图2中阴影部分面积A，即就是说：&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;磁场能量的大小等于磁化曲线b和纵轴所围成的面积大小。图1中，假定磁路&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;各部分的面积相等，磁芯各部分的磁场强度为Hm，气隙部分的磁场强度为Hg，由全电流定律得：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.szsanyi.com/storage/521/weixin/1803/21/d021ecacfae503543427fd22dbd1e4be.png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; list-style: none; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; text-indent: 0em; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;11式右边第一项是磁芯中的磁场能量，第二项是气隙部分的磁场能量，分别用&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;Wi和Wg表示；那么：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.szsanyi.com/storage/521/weixin/1803/21/c0ab976f129f0e391499f4b97a5f1863.png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; list-style: none; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; text-indent: 0em; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;图3中，曲线m表示图1电感器无气隙时的磁化曲线，曲线g表示有气隙时的磁&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;化曲线。图中，面积Am表示储存在磁芯部分的磁场能量；面积Ag表示储存在气隙&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;/&gt;部分的磁场能量。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '1526550572', null, '0', '1');
INSERT INTO `sc_articles` VALUES ('33', '“食指与中指”在开关电源设计中的妙用？', '三一精工', '“食指与中指”在开关电源设计中的妙用？', '“食指与中指”在开关电源设计中的妙用？', '1', '&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;a data-mid=&quot;1&quot; href=&quot;http://www.szsanyi.com/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration-line: none;&quot;&gt;开关电源&lt;/a&gt;是功率型产品，发热量比较大，电源工程师在设计开关电源时需要做热设计和温升的测试，规模较大的公司都有自己的专业测试仪器比如热成像仪，但是对于一些微小型的公司肯定是没有这些设备的，只能用点温计。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;但在电源调试中用如果没有热成像的话用点温计不是太方便，下面小编最简单的用手指预估元器件的温度，手指探温度时一定要记得先关电哦。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;在最终温升定量的测试必须用点温仪来测试！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;当被元器件温度在&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;30度&lt;/strong&gt;左右时，&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;手感微温有舒适感。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;当被元器件温度在&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;40度&lt;/strong&gt;左右时，&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;如摸高烧病人。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;当被元器件温度在&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;50度&lt;/strong&gt;左右时，&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;手感较烫，长时间的接触可能有汗感；&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;当被元器件温度在&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;60度&lt;/strong&gt;左右时，&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;手感很烫，一般可以忍受10秒左右；&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;当被元器件温度在&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;70度&lt;/strong&gt;左右时，&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;手指的忍耐力只有3秒左右，出现灼痛感，且接触部位很快变红；&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;当被元器件温度在&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;80度&lt;/strong&gt;左右时，&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;能瞬间接触，且痛感加剧（麻辣火烧），如果触摸时间过长，会发生烫伤。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;检查方法：用右手的食指，中指和无名指并拢，以其指背的中节部位用弹性点触的方法轻触被测表面，断定对皮肤无损伤时，方能用手指肚来断定温度。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;特别注意：皮肤被烫伤的临界温度是55摄氏度，即超过55摄氏度皮肤就有可能烫伤。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;其实温度的预估可谓是五花八门，有的用手摸，有的贴温度试纸，甚至有的用鼻子闻。工程师你对于预估元器件温度有没有一些脑洞大开的想法？&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '1526549808', null, '0', '1');
INSERT INTO `sc_articles` VALUES ('34', '电源原理分析、波形分析、应力计算、回路布局', '三一精工', '电源原理分析、波形分析、应力计算、回路布局', '电源原理分析、波形分析、应力计算、回路布局', '1', '&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;目录&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;1、Flyback变换器工作模态分析；&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;2、Flyback关键波形分析；&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;3、RCD吸收电路设计及开关管应力；&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;4、从噪音回路看布线要点。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;5、基于实际项目，原创反激&lt;a data-mid=&quot;1&quot; href=&quot;http://www.szsanyi.com/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration-line: none;&quot;&gt;开关电源&lt;/a&gt;视频教程曝光&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;&quot;&gt;Flyback 变换器模态分析&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.szsanyi.com/storage/521/weixin/1803/21/a08e9c49c353a88e07ce798da2ec3a79.png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto